Release mdbreact v.4.8.6

Improves & fixes:
- new Edge Header Plugin
- new examples in demo pages
- Pagination - new size property

Release mdbreact v.4.8.7

Updated:
- React 16.7.0
- ReactDOM 16.7.0
- Webpack 4.28.1
- SASS/CSS - synchronized with MDB v.4.6.0

Release mdbreact v.4.9.0

Major change:
- Font Awesome updated to v.5.6.3

Improves & fixes:
- Refactered MDBInput component (now it can be used as the
controlled/uncontrolled input)
- MDBDataTable has gain lots of new props, which allows to adjust
entries, pagination, column's sorting peculiarity, click events
- New axamples in E-commerce
- New prop 'zoom' for MDBCards
- SVG imports improved,
- Demo pages fully updated to be consisten with syntax guidelines
- Repaired MDBSelect's search
- MDBDatePicker slightly rebuild, so now it can be used as the
controlled/uncontrolled input
- Bug fixes in MDBCol
- MDBButtonFixed - repaired size prop and onClick handler
- Updated SASS/CSS - synchronized with MDB v.4.6.1

Release mdbreact v.4.10.0

What has changed:
- Bootstrap was updated (bootstrap-css-only v.4.2.1)
- Switched production module bundler from Webpack to Rollup
- Improved tree-shaking support
- Updated SASS/CSS - synchronized with MDB v.4.7.0
- Carousel - inner syntax updated
- New blog components
- Modal- fixed modal behaviour with hidden backdrop
- Cardimage - removed default zoom property
- Datatable - refactored key binding of Page Items
- Switch - swapped default labels
- Select - refactored Search element logic

Release mdbreact v.4.11.0

What has changed:

- new smoothSccroll

Release mdbreact v.4.11.1

- updated the package with the newest 4.3.1 version of Bootstrap
- added Bootstrap Responsive Font Size settings
- added popovers with images

Release mdbreact v.4.12.0

Major change:
- react-popper update,
- new usage of Tooltips & Popovers,

Improves:
- SideNav - added slim prop which collapses sidebar vertically
and shortcut prop which defines categoreis names in slim mode,
- SideNav - now is scrollable by default, added swipe-out func,
added showOverlay prop, fixed and reposnsive (which switch those
modes accordingly),
- Tooltip - now supports fixed components,
- Admin Dashboard - fixed icons alignment,
- Select - fixed issue with search and icons, updated render
methods, added group separator line,
- Tooltips & Popovers - rebuilt form scratch,
- Dropdown - refactor due to popper update, better aligned menu,
- FileInput - cleaned up template, added flip property (flips
buttons to the other side of the input),
- Autocomplete - rebuilt from scratch, added keyboard control,
- updated SASS/CSS - synchronized with MDB v.4.7.5

Release mdbreact v.4.13.0

Changelog:

peerDependencies, updated Rollup config,
- Select (controlled select) - added selectAll functionality,
- Dropdown - added dropleft and dropright props,

- SmoothScroll - added lots of new style and position properties,
- View - added proeprty fixed,
- Added lots of new examples in documentation,
- Updated SASS/CSS - synchronized with MDB v.4.7.6

Release mdbreact v4.17.0

 Changelog:
 -Carousel - added touch gesture support;
  fixed count of showing items in Multi-item carousel when use on small screens,
 -DataTable - added new property barReverse: swaps position of 'search' and 'show entries' elements,
 -DatePicker - fixed issue when click on the opened DatePicker caused closing the modal,
 -Select - added new property selectAllClassName: adds class to the Select All option;
  fixed issue when click on the label or disabled option caused closing the list of options,

Release mdbreact v4.18.0

Changelog:
New:
-InputGroup - added new component,

Generate version v.4.23.0
Changelog:

New:
Tooltip (pro) - Added pro variation of component,
Parallax (pro) - Added new pro component,
Typography - Added new component. With this component, you can easily create notes, headings, and other elements. This component allows using different typography tags like h1 - h6, ul, p to create elements with bootstrap's typography classes like display-1, h1-responsive, h1-h6, etc. ,
Box - Added new component. With this component, you can easily replace every tag in your JSX files like div, p, span, video, etc. This component allows using different display styles like flex/block/inline, margins, and paddings. To create elements with props we are using custom bootstrap classes and our custom styles from MDB. https://mdbootstrap.com/docs/react/layout/box/
Gallery - Added new component. This component allows you to easily create an image gallery with a forwarding object to the props gallery. ,
CardVideo - Added new CardVideo component allows you to add full responsive video container into your card;

Fixed:
Button Fixed - Remove bug with hover empty space upper of the button,
Stepper - Fix Font Awesome icon props at MDBStepper and MDBStep component,
Tabs - Fix demo app example;

Improved:
DataTable (pro) - New filter property for DataTable,
Full Page Callendar (plugin) - Change title input fromtext to textarea,
Lightbox - Added tabIndex property for object property of image and now you can focus image with the tab key.,
Lightbox - Added keyboard events for open close and change image;
